**Description for “HTML Pro” (by Mahrus Ali)**

HTML Pro is a complete collection of professional-grade HTML templates, snippets, and best practices—designed for developers who want clean, efficient, and scalable front-end code. This repository covers everything from basic HTML structures to advanced semantic layouts, accessibility standards, and SEO-friendly markup.

Whether you're a beginner sharpening your HTML skills or a seasoned developer building production-ready pages, **HTML Pro** offers well-documented examples, reusable components, and real-world patterns to speed up your workflow.

**Features:**

* Semantic and accessible HTML5 examples
* Responsive and modern layouts
* Pre-built templates for portfolios, landing pages, and dashboards
* Organized file structure for scalability
* Easy to integrate with CSS frameworks and JavaScript

**Perfect for:**
Web developers, designers, and learners aiming to master HTML the professional way.
